Class MgCoordinateSystemGeodeticAnalyticalTransformDefParams

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.osgeo.mapguide.MgObject

  • public class MgCoordinateSystemGeodeticAnalyticalTransformDefParams
extends MgCoordinateSystemGeodeticTransformDefParams
    This class holds all parameters that are specific to analytical geodetic transformation methods, e.g. geocentric transformation, molodensky etc.
